[I] Extract files from any kind of container formats

[T] Unblob is an accurate, fast, and easy-to-use extraction suite. It parses
[T] unknown binary blobs for more than 30 different archive, compression, and
[T] file-system formats, extracts their content recursively, and carves out
[T] unknown chunks that have not been accounted for.

[U] https://unblob.org/

[A] ONEKEY GmbH
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

